/* Non - Real Real Time */
1. To Compile
	g++ motionDetection.cpp `pkg-config opencv --cflags --libs` -o track

2. To Run
	./track

/* Real Time */
1. Install liblitmus library and replace the base_task.c inside liblitmus/bin file by the given base_task.c file

2. Replace the Makefile in liblitmus folder with the Make file given

3. To Compile - Inside liblitmus Folder
	make
4. To Run
	./base_task
